                "correct_answer": "is"
              },
              {
                "instruction": "Complete the sentences using am, is, and are.",
                "text": "I _____ a teacher.",
                "options": [
                  "am",
                  "is",
                  "are"
                ],
                "correct_answer": "am"
              },
              {
                "instruction": "Complete the sentences using am, is, and are.",
